OL,6,FOn their website, PayByPhone says
OL,7,Ftheir mobile app has "revolutionised
OL,8,Fstreet parking payments by offering a
OL,9,Fdigital payment option," but that
OL,10,F"this convenience has also given
OL,11,Fcertain cybercriminals ideas."
OL,13,F"We have taken a hard stance on this
OL,14,Fby no longer providing our Council and
OL,15,Fparking operating partners with QR
OL,16,Fcodes as a means for their motorists
OL,17,Fto make payments in the UK," their
OL,18,Fwebsite says.
